TXL Example Specification
-------------------------

Name:	
	RStoFB.Txl

Description:
	One of a suite of six database schema translation systems
	to automatically transform database schemas between data models
	to assist in database migration and/or multidatabase integration.
	This particular transform translates relational (SQL/DDL)
	database schemas to ER (Entity-Relationship) schemas in Prolog
	factbase form.  
	
	This system is described in detail in "Schema Translation 
	Using Structural Transformation", R. Abu-Hamdeh, J.R. Cordy and 
	T.P. Martin, Proc. CASCON'94, IBM Centre for Advanced Studies 
	1994 Conference, Toronto, November 1994, pp. 202-215.

Author:
   	R. Abu-Hamde

Affiliation:
	Queen's University, Kingston, Canada

Date:
	August 1993
	Revised August 1995

Example:
	txl consulatant.RS RStoFB.Txl
